description.plain:
Dynoro is a DJ from Vilnius, the capital city of Lithuania, a small country in Eastern Europe. Getting supported by the record label Lithuania HQ has helped him to gain more recognition.

Dynoro is mostly known for his breakout hit in 2018, “In My Mind,” which has gained over 700 million clicks on multiple platforms and ruled many charts for a long time.
